    "body": "When setting `cluster.routing.allocation.disable_allocation`, it causes new indices primary shards to not be allocated. By default, new indices created should allow to, at the very least, allocate primary shards so they become operations. A new setting, `cluster.routing.allocation.disable_new_allocation`, allows to also disable \"new\" allocations.\n", 
